window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The war didn’t end when the Gehenna retreated. It just got quieter—and quieter is worse.</p> <p>On Mars, in the alien-human fortress we call The Roar, we’re preparing for their return.</p> <p>Training harder, leveling up, and waiting for the silence to shatter.</p> <p>I’m James Thorne, Psyker, Cleansed, and despite hitting Level 10, someone who can’t catch a break.</p>"; 
